{
  "bookId": "heshanggong-laozi",
  "num": 59,
  "title": "第五十九章（守道）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "治人，"
    },
    {
      "text": "事天，"
    },
    {
      "text": "莫若嗇。"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫為嗇，是謂早服。"
    },
    {
      "text": "早服謂之重積德。"
    },
    {
      "text": "重積德則無不剋，"
    },
    {
      "text": "無不剋則莫知其極，"
    },
    {
      "text": "莫知其極可以有國。"
    },
    {
      "text": "有國之母，可以長久。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是謂深根固蒂，"
    },
    {
      "text": "長生久視之道。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 3
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "謂人君治理人民。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 3
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "事，用也。當用天道，順四時。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "嗇，愛惜也。 治國者當愛民財，不為奢泰。 治身者當愛精氣，不為放逸。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "早，先也。服，得也。 夫獨愛民財，愛精氣，則能先得天道也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "先得天道，是謂重積得於己也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "剋，勝也。重積德於己，則無不勝。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "無不剋勝，則莫知有知己德之窮極也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "莫知己德者有極，則可以有社稷，為民致福。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "國身同也。母，道也。 人能保身中之道，使精氣不勞，五神不苦，則可以長久。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人能以氣為根，以精為蒂，如樹根不深則拔，蒂不堅則落。 言當深藏其氣，固守其精，使無漏泄。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "深根固蒂者，乃長生久視之道。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
